trans-unit.source: Describes a geometry using drawing commands.
trans-unit.target: Beskriver en geometri bruker tegning kommandoer.

trans-unit.source: This class is used with the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometry"></xref> class to create a lightweight geometry that does not support data binding, animation, or modification.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes med den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometry"> </xref> klassen for å opprette en lett geometri som ikke støtter databinding, animasjon eller endringen.

trans-unit.source: Draws an arc to the specified point.
trans-unit.target: Tegner en bue til det angitte punktet.

trans-unit.source: This method uses the end point of the previous segment as its starting point.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden bruker sluttpunktet for forrige segmentet som startpunktet.

trans-unit.source: If this is the first segment in a figure, it uses the point specified by the <xref:System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometryContext.BeginFigure%2A> method as its start point.
trans-unit.target: Hvis dette er det første segmentet i et tall, bruker punkt som er angitt av den <xref:System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometryContext.BeginFigure%2A>metoden som startpunktet.</xref:System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometryContext.BeginFigure%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometry> cannot be serialized if it contains a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Transform> or any non-stroked or unfilled segments.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometry>kan ikke serialiseres hvis den inneholder en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Transform>eller noen ikke streket eller være uten fyll segmenter.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Transform> </xref:System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometry>

trans-unit.source: The destination point for the end of the arc.
trans-unit.target: Målet punktet for slutten på buen.

trans-unit.source: The radii (half the width and half the height) of an oval whose perimeter is used to draw the angle.
trans-unit.target: Radier (halv bredde og halvparten av høyden) til en ellipsen der ytre brukes til å tegne vinkelen.

trans-unit.source: If the oval is very rounded in all directions, the arc will be rounded, if it is nearly flat, so will the arc.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ellipsen er svært avrundet i alle retninger, buen avrundet, hvis den er nesten flate, så vil buen.

trans-unit.source: For example, a very large width and height would represent a very large oval, which would give a slight curvature for the angle.
trans-unit.target: En svært bredde og høyde kan for eksempel representere en svært ellipsen som vil gi en liten forskjellig type for vinkelen.

trans-unit.source: The rotation angle of the oval that specifies the curve.
trans-unit.target: Rotasjonsvinkelen for ellipsen som angir buen.

trans-unit.source: The curvature of the arc can be rotated with this parameter.
trans-unit.target: Forskjellig type for arc kan roteres med denne parameteren.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to draw the arc greater than 180 degrees; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>til å tegne buen større enn 180 grader. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A value that indicates whether the arc is drawn in the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.SweepDirection"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Media.SweepDirection"></xref> direction.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir om buen tegnes den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.SweepDirection"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Windows.Media.SweepDirection"> </xref> retning.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to make the segment stroked when a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Pen"></xref> is used to render the segment; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>foreta segmentet streket når en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Pen"> </xref> er brukt til å gjengi segmentet; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the starting point for a new figure.
trans-unit.target: Angir startpunktet for et nytt tall.

trans-unit.source: By calling this method multiple times, you can create multiple figures (self-contained geometric shapes) within this <xref:System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometryContext>.
trans-unit.target: Ved å kalle denne metoden flere ganger, kan du opprette flere tallene (uavhengige geometrisk figurer) i <xref:System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometryContext>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.StreamGeometryContext>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Point"> </xref> der tallet starter.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to use the area contained by this figure for hit-testing, rendering, and clipping; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>bruke området finnes i dette tallet for testing av treff gjengivelse og beskjæring; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to close the figure; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>lukke tallet; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: For example, if two connecting lines are drawn, and `isClosed` is set to <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>, the drawing will just be of two lines but if `isClosed` is set to <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, the two lines will be closed to create a triangle.
trans-unit.target: Hvis to tilkobling linjer er tegnet, for eksempel og `isClosed` er satt til <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>, blir bare tegning av to linjene men hvis `isClosed` er satt til <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>, de to linjene lukkes for å opprette en trekant.

trans-unit.source: Draws a Bezier curve to the specified point.

trans-unit.source: A cubic Bezier curve is defined by a start point, end point, and two control points.
trans-unit.target: En cubic Bezier kurve er definert av et startpunkt, sluttpunkt og to kontrollpunkt.

trans-unit.source: The first control point determines the curvature of the first half of the segment, and the second control point determines the curvature of the second half of the segment.
trans-unit.target: Det første kontrollpunktet bestemmer forskjellig type for den første halvparten av segmentet, og andre kontrollpunkt bestemmer forskjellig type for den andre halvparten av segmentet.
